MongoDB CRUD Operations by "mongodb" library

1) create the directory (folder)
    
    Ex.
      MongoDb_CRUD


2) download the libraries by using "npm" or 'yarn' tool

    => 1)mongodb    2)@types/mongodb

          -used to connect ot mongodb database
        1) express     2)@types/express


    => body-parser @types/body-parser

          - used to receive the data from 'cliend'  applications


> yarnd add mongodb @types/mongodb express @types/express cors @types/cors body-parses



